A 25-year-old man from Kiel-Kiel Farm, Dannhauser, KwaZulu-Natal has been brutally murdered and left in an open veld.The deceased, Nathi Vilakazi, was stabbed nine times and his intestines were found outside his body. His throat was also cut, the Northern Natal Courier reported.His body was found on May 14. We are appealing to anyone with information concerning this brutal murder to please contact Dannhauser SAPS on 034 621 6500, Const Nyembe urged. Caxton News ServiceRead original story on northernnatalcourier.co.za